{"tid":1849444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大研製疫苗 料需時一年","createTime":"2020-01-29T05:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T06:22:27.000Z","uid":248290,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"388b299dcc884f94d2e2824b4f58fe08e0f0ea95","tid":1849444,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎暫時既無針對性藥物，亦無疫苗，難醫又難防。由香港大學微生物學系講座教授袁國勇帶領的團隊，在取得深圳兩名確診病人的病毒基因排序，及從香港第一宗確診個案相關樣本分離出病毒株後，發現利用病毒的表面蛋白可入侵人體細胞，有能力預防引起武漢肺炎的新型冠狀病毒，並正嘗試研製含有已弱化病毒的吸入式「減活疫苗」，惟仍要待通過動物實驗及人類臨床實驗，才能推出，需時或至少一年。<br />\n<br />\n袁指，計劃在早年已開始研製的流感吸入式減活疫苗中，加入新型冠狀病毒元素，若成功，相信疫苗對流感和新型冠狀病毒均有保護效用，而研製疫苗時會非常小心，盡量減少可能的副作用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/港大研製疫苗-料需時-年-214500149.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%A0%94%E8%A3%BD%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E6%96%99%E9%9C%80%E6%99%82-%E5%B9%B4-214500149.html&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=7f2813c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/港大研製疫苗-料需時-年-214500149.html</a><br />\n<br />\n要 一年時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef83d0298ebf9a8d287155ac0727887b2479b866","tid":1849444,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=3d9af55c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度簽得七七八八<br />\n麻煩fb tg發出去搵新客源簽"},{"